Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.06,0:00:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}据说人死后
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.62,0:00:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就能登入极乐
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我却不这么认为
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}逝者的生命一定在生者的心间旅行
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.93,0:00:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}化为回忆…流淌
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如同我爸爸妈妈那般
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}寄宿在我们的心中
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.75,0:00:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.20,0:00:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这些也终将消却
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.00,0:00:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以人们才会想留下些什么
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.16,0:00:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为了不被忘却
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.24,0:00:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}有照出来吗…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.23,0:00:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}取景器一片黑的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不被忘却
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.77,0:01:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真美的手
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.33,0:01:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.68,0:01:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 我为什么会…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…昨天是…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.76,0:01:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天是想试试高感光胶卷
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.81,0:01:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.88,0:01:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再不起来要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.36,0:01:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去国外出差？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 不过就三个月
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.29,0:03:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去哪？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.18,0:03:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}玻利维亚
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说是人手不够
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 小海
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你说姐姐该去吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你想去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能自己做饭
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.51,0:03:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且又快暑假了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.15,0:03:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一个人了别太放纵了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还有
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃相不好！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回来的时候会去买点东西
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过七点前会回来的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了 走好哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是 走好
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一个人生活…吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个位置不错
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}红色的…头发？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.42,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}究竟是…为什么…会这么显眼的？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是不是…有哪里搞错了？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊 地方找好了吗？海
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天不是去找地方了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拿着那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 昨天只是去测试胶卷…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要拍电影了吧？导演
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是随便拍拍 不知不觉的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么啊 我还想着来帮帮你呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过不过…如果哲郎同学在电影里上镜的话
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.49,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女生们肯定高兴死了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就算啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说回来 美樱你才是要试试吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海 美樱主演可以吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正值夏日 和偶像的印像录影集很相配呢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.09,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么样？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又不用花多少钱也不用剧本的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会…会被盯着看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会被乱想
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 男生的欲望一览无遗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.85,0:05:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}确实想做些什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么是指？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然还太不清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是想
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊 毕竟
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们可是高中生啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又是夏天
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 感觉是得做些什么
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 我还在想你在拍什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来喜欢那种类型的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}摄影机还在拍哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…那个 不是这样…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.17,0:06:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才那人确实和柑菜是正相反的类型呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你是什么意思
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔 有很多
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以说是什么啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说了有很多含义嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那算什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.71,0:06:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说来你这人…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了算了 都冷静下来 柑菜
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}当然 当时的我并没有发觉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}迟到了很抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我从今天起转学到贵校
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫贵月一夏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}属于我们的电视剧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已然开始
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}镜头的画面正流转着
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在以前的学校有参加什么社团活动么？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.07,0:07:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这时候转学很少见呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}头发的颜色好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有在和谁交往吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快散开
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.71,0:07:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一群饿狼
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎么了啊 山乃
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正是同学
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们啊 如果不老实点…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可会倒大霉哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天中午吃什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了对了 昨天的电视啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫山乃柠檬
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.87,0:07:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…我是贵月一夏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦…有什么奇怪的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们看来能成为好朋友呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}山乃同学
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫柠檬就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那柠檬 能问你一件事吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么啊？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么你穿着不一样的校服呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}秘密
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可告人的秘密
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说回来 你这饮食真是不均衡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 哪里不对了？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}碳水化合物和水份
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是挺OK的组合嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什么地方奇怪了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这个人很奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哪里奇怪 怎么奇怪了？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是这里
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}名字叫贵月一夏
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天正式转入三年级A班
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身高160cm
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.56,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}体重41kg
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.50,0:08:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}三围从上到下是 92-58-88
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}鞋码是…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎样查到的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个嘛…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.34,0:09:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老师 转校过来的那位三年级学姐的个人资料…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同学你真是的 别告诉其他人哦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概就像这样
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不就是赤裸裸的犯罪嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.12,0:09:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.61,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客气
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们在这里干什么
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.86,0:09:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哟 吃过了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.37,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来如此 又想偷拍吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.28,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是啊 那只是偶然照到的…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.20,0:09:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你烦人！
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.15,0:09:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说真的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 打你啊 快说真话啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.93,0:09:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很痛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.91,0:09:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啰嗦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在吃醋呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.14,0:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 就这么定了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不行啊 而且又没有带可爱的泳装来
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.30,0:09:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海 我们走
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去是…去哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 我的饮食哪里…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}午安
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思 能占用你一点时间吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 哲郎 你想要干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦好啦 交给我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…没什么…那个…有什么事？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…你是今天刚转校过来的贵月一夏学姐吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是一年级的石垣哲郎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他是雾岛海人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.95,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}实际上我们几个人在一起拍着电影玩儿
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后 学姐…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以的话 能出演我们的电影吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你在突然说些什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…如果我可以的话
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请务必让我帮忙
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开始运转的事物 就不能轻易停下来
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.12,0:10:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}艾拉薇莉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也要参加
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.96,0:11:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是三年级的山乃柠檬
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在自己也全然不觉的时候……
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.20,0:11:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}三年级?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.20,0:11:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}高年级的？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.54,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}镜头就开始运转了…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀…原本只是想随便试试的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.04,0:11:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真没想到会成功啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏学姐 太好说话了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真是太乱来了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想做就做 这是我的作风
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 心情真是不错啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这景色也真是别致
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像个老头子似的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐呐 真的要拍吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}电影
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都已经那么和学姐说过了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会…会拍些什么呢…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那些就交给小小只的柠檬学姐吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毕竟…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}电影的内容就交给我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正好有本为卢卡斯写的书
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好莱坞顶级导演？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.23,0:12:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是自己要写吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她都这么说了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么…我也参加
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}后台工作人员的话我也能来帮下忙吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不 美樱还是出演吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这不行的不行的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么 有什么不行？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.61,0:12:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}电影…啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.27,0:12:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}导演 能指导我的…演技吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贴身扶腰教哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是手把手啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}手取り足取り被他說成是腰 這裡取意譯
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在笑些什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说这是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.05,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.85,0:12:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个呀 这个
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.11,0:12:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 有什么吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个 不是吻痕吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.57,0:12:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.81,0:12:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…看到了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.56,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是什么啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以说了是吻痕
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天拍摄的时候被虫咬了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 这种事我根本不记得
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…好像默认了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道有印像了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂喂 你到底在拍点什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都说了不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}农民的地租经验
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.51,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}市民的自由言论集会…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.25,0:13:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和别国的平等条约的缔结要求
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起来很精神
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}根据这三点主张…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那明天的休息日 大家就碰个面
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}举行电影开拍大会
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.39,0:13:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬学姐她们就由我来联系了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.68,0:13:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么我就先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天见
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.63,0:13:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.64,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么我也…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 当心点哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别看他那样其实是很期待的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.34,0:14:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.12,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.36,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没错
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.81,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做了什么多余的事吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了 契机越多越好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这种从上往下看的感觉 总让人觉得恼火
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在那飘飘然个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 电影吗…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样应该没什么错
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.95,0:14:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.92,0:14:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫海人 雾岛海人
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 海人同学
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 为什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 我从那边看到你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是在…钓鱼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 这是我的兴趣
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这虽然是很好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这条河 没有鱼哦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你告诉我
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能帮上忙就好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我对这附近还不熟 真是帮我大忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.46,0:15:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…钓鱼的话 再稍微走一段路就能见到一条大点的河了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那里的话就一定能…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么我就先…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 以后还请多多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.65,0:15:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}彼此彼此 请多关照
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做了件让自己遗憾的事吗…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是再多交流交流
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么说呢 就像是…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说白了就是
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.87,0:16:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏学姐是一个人搬来这里的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厉害 怎么会知道的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看你手上的行李就知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}简单的推理而已
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后我又进一步推理了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐因为没有住的地方 非常困扰
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又猜中了真厉害
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和要入住的地方间发生了什么意外
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正确 正确
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实现在正流落街头
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那种地方钓鱼就是最好的证据
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又正确啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.78,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要来…我家吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.20,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是一夏学姐愿意的话
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}当然了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.85,0:16:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顺便一提 这里就是我家
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 好大的房子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是去世的奶奶的房子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大的对我来说太过了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多住学姐一个根本不算什么
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.05,0:17:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是太棒了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.31,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且 住一起的话就能进行电影的演技指导了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.33,0:17:17.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「手取り腰取り」其實應該是「手取り足取り」 含義是即使細小的環節也能照顧到。
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这才贴身扶腰指导啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我觉得是手把手啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是 现实吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 从什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}蛮久前了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.05,0:17:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我真是很困扰呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.30,0:17:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个… 你指的是？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？ 就是“不来我家吗”
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 从这里开始的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.44,0:17:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…等一下 刚才那是我的妄想…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对 是自言自语
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且我姐姐还在家里
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.60,0:17:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然带女孩子回家的话 有点太唐突了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…说的也是呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉啊 这样勉强你
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.82,0:18:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶…那个…学姐要去哪呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.39,0:18:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在这附近找一个比较方便露宿的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…没办法了！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦…七海姐
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 是柑菜酱啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.49,0:18:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是少见呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这么早 在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}工作已经交班了 然后还有别的事
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.01,0:18:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别的事？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.03,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 但是它却突然不动了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.90,0:18:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 对了！柑菜酱能不能帮我一个忙呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你先在那坐一会儿吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}行李的话就先…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好重
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是怎么带它到这里的啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是重…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.48,0:18:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然很重但是使劲拉就可以有窍门的！
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唉 总之只能住一晚哦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有今晚…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.49,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 我是第一次进男孩子的房间
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.89,0:19:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 这…这样啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 不能再这样悠闲了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.36,0:19:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我待会儿给你送晚饭…哦不…还有姐姐大概七点回来…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在就先洗个澡吧 换洗的衣服在那里面吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱…歉…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那箱子里…装的是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.14,0:19:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…这个是洗发水
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}睡衣…睡衣…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐的睡袍…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姑且算是搞定衣服了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}衣…衣服就放在洗衣机上了…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢啦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.27,0:20:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用把门打开啦！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}离七点还早呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天这算什么啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.53,0:20:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和学姐相遇 决定做电影…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐不知为什么到我的家里来…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.87,0:20:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之我也先收拾下行李换换衣服吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.15,0:20:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 这个也得收一下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么回事 这里被虫子刺了一下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.16,0:20:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…怎么回事
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学 这个衣服啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.20,0:20:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学！？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学！海人同学！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎么了…振作一下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.35,0:21:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…细胞的代谢变得…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.46,0:21:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了 起作用了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.28,0:21:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起…对不起啊 已经没事儿了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是帮大忙了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.67,0:21:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你 柑菜酱
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没什么啦 不过…要出差3个月啊？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.72,0:21:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 海人就拜托柑菜你啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算去一起住也没关系啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 那种事！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.67,0:22:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为姐姐会支持柑菜酱你啦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什…什么意思嘛！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊呀 还装傻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…这个…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.00,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐的眼睛好像又有点不舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.36,0:22:19.91,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像光线太强烈了 看到了海人和一个女的抱在一起的幻觉…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.31,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那算什么嘛 好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.63,0:22:23.60,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.87,0:22:32.82,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.87,0:22:41.39,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在 在 在 在做什么啊！？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.10,0:22:42.76,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.98,0:22:43.92,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总之你们先分开！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.90,0:22:47.32,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然这是理所当然的事 但是我却没有发觉
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.84,0:22:55.53,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们所知道的…我们所留下的…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.01,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想让你知晓
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.63,0:23:34.90,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我那些…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.79,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}满溢而出的回忆
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.30,0:23:38.32,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但它却停不住脚步
