Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:01.83,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}越过流云的浮影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:04.48,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}绘出想你的冲动
